REQUIREMENTS

  pdfLaTeX typesetting engine 1.30 or later

  LaTeX packages
     verbatim, graphicx, ifthen, calc, etoolbox, xkeyval
  SAS 9.2 or later

See the StatRep User's Guide, included with this package, for complete details.

